290
00:50:20,240 --> 00:50:20,877
Nothing!

291
00:50:21,080 --> 00:50:22,513
Did she agree to go with you?

292
00:50:22,720 --> 00:50:23,789
Let's go.

293
00:50:49,000 --> 00:50:50,479
