449
01:17:15,240 --> 01:17:16,468
Are you feeling OK?

450
01:17:16,680 --> 01:17:18,557
I'm all right.

451
01:17:21,680 --> 01:17:22,749
Want a lift?

452
01:19:41,720 --> 01:19:43,073
